snippet.title: Ribeye Charlie's -- Horror Game  -- 2018 -- VHS Cap
snippet.description:
The next entry in our "5 minutes of horror" series. 

After leaving your wallet behind, you return to Ribeye Charlie's house of steak and pasta to retrieve it. The restaurant is closed but the front door is open. You step in.

Download Ribeye Charlie's: https://circlestarsoft.itch.io/ribeye-charlies

Twitter: https://twitter.com/CircleStarSoft

Circle Star Software indie horror game on itchio
Music by: David O'Neil (Thank You!)

#indie #horror #retro #vhs #80s
